textBeforeTable: Overview of the finances of The NetBSD Foundation for the year 2004 Starting with the year 2004 the Board of Directors of The NetBSD Foundation publishes yearly overviews of the financial situation of the NetBSD Project. The primary source of income currently is donations. Two separate accounts, one in USD and the other in EUR, are maintained because The NetBSD Foundation receives donations in both currencies. Conversions between currencies are only performed when necessary.
